Nge7 25. Ke2 Ba4 26. g4 Rd8 27. Kf3 Nc6 28. Ne2 Bb5 29. Nc3 Nxc3 30. Rxc3 Ne7
31. Rb2 g6 32. h4 Bc6 33. Rcb3 Nd5 34. h5 Rd7 35. h6 Rc8 36. Rd2 Rcc7 37. Rd4
Kf8 38. Rb2 Ke8 39. Bd2 Bb5 40. a4 Bc6 41. Ba5 Rc8 42. Kg3 Kf8 43. Rbd2 Kg8 44.
f5 {In the following correspondence game White did not manage to win in the
